name: Takjil Delight Cupcakes
description:
After holding your thirst and hunger all day, why not grab some “takjil” cupcakes?

This pack consists of delightful three cupcakes inspired by Indonesian signature ice. The “Teler” is an avocado cake and cream with brown sugar jelly under the coconut-tasted frosting cream and jackfruit chips. The “Campur” is a mix-berry vanilla cake with frambozen cream and fresh cuts of nata de coco, apple, melon, and strawberry. While the “Pisang Ijo” is a red velvet ombre cake with vanilla cream and candied banana on the top.
